trans-unit.source: Represents a reference in a discovery document to a service description.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en referanse i discovery-dokumentet til en beskrivelse av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: XML Web services discovery involves discovering the available Web Services given an URL.
trans-unit.target: XML-Web services discovery innebærer å oppdage tilgjengelig webtjenestene gitt en URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: The URL usually points to a discovery document, which typically has a.disco file name extension.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen peker vanligvis til discovery-dokumentet, som vanligvis har a.disco filtype.

trans-unit.source: Within a discovery document are references to information about the existance of XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder referanser til informasjon om eksistens for XML-webtjenester discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: These references can refer to service descriptions, XML Schema Definition language (XSD) schemas or other discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Disse referansene kan referere til tjenestebeskrivelser av, XML-skjemadefinisjon språket (XSD) skjemaer eller andre discovery-dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: This class represents a reference to a Service Description.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen representerer en referanse til en beskrivelse av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Within a discovery document, a reference to a Service Description is contained within a `contractRef` XML element.
trans-unit.target: I et søkedataelement-dokument, en referanse til en tjenestebeskrivelsen er innenfor en `contractRef` XML-elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `contractRef` XML element has two attributes: `ref` and `docRef`.
trans-unit.target: Den `contractRef` XML-elementet har to attributter: `ref` og `docRef`.

trans-unit.source: The `contractRef` element must have an XML namespace matching the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Namespace> constant, whereas the `ref` and `docRef` attributes are placed in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Ref%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.DocRef%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den `contractRef` -elementet må ha en XML-navneområde samsvarende den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Namespace>konstant, mens den `ref` og `docRef` attributter plasseres i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Ref%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.DocRef%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.DocRef%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Ref%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference.Namespace>
